description:
Give even your largest rooms a boost of flameless fragrance with Glade Wax Melts. Cubes of scented wax melt release true-to-life fragrance — filling your home with a scent you’ll love. Glade Wax Melts are available in a wide variety of your favorite Glade scents. Rosy Cheeks. Warmth. Delightful apple notes with comforting spices of nutmeg and cinnamon. A touch of berries notes, balanced with creamy musk. Come inside; feels like cozy.

DIRECTIONS FOR USE: 1. Remove one Glade wax melt from packaging and place in center of a clean and empty warmer bowl. Do not use more than one melt at a time. 2. Read and follow instructions provided with warmer. Warmer will melt wax, releasing fragrance into air. 3. When melt no longer releases fragrance, stop use of melt and warmer. WAX REMOVAL INSTRUCTIONS: 1. Allow wax to cool completely and harden. 2. Pop wax out of warmer dish. If needed, use blunt wood or rubber tool to push wax out of warmer dish. 3. Dispose of wax in trash, do not place wax down drain.

USES: USES: Fill any room with flameless fragrances.

description:
Continuous fragrance for any size room is just an outlet away with Glade PlugIns Scented Oils. With each fragrance refill lasting up to 30 days, on low setting, simply plug in the warmer for long-lasting fragrance that’s adjustable to fill any room in your home with your favorite Glade fragrances.
Sunshine. Flirtation. Golden rays of light on a perfectly crisp apple, surrounded by dahlia blossoms and green meadow grass layered on soft cashmere musk and woods. A sparkling walk outside filled with laughter. Feels like young love.

DIRECTIONS FOR USE: To use, rotate warmer's electrical plug, if needed. Unscrew cap from fragrance bottle and insert into warmer. Insert warmer UPRIGHT into outlet. Adjust warmer intensity to desired setting. When empty, replace fragrance oil bottle with Glade PlugIns Scented Oil refills only. Do not use any other refills in Glade PlugIns Scented Oil Warmers. Fragrance oils may collect on warmer unit over time. To clean, remove warmer unit from electrical outlet and wipe with dry cloth. Wash hands after handling.

USES: Use in any room for continuous lasting fragrance.
